lead_paragraph: The ex-girlfriend of Johnny Manziel, a quarterback for the Cleveland Browns football team, was questioned by police in Fort Worth, Texas, over a possible disturbance involving the athlete, police said.

headline.print_headline: NFL Player Manziel Investigated Over Possible Assault: Police
